name: IMMZ.DT.05.Hib
description: if child or person has not been vaccinated, give Hib vaccine between 4 and 18 months

action.title: Immunize Patient for Hib - No Doses
action.description: Provide Hib immunizations – using the "Hib Vaccine immunization – NO PREVIOUS" schedule (1 dose scheme)

expression.description: "Hib vaccine immunization history" = "No-doses and > 12 months old and no known allergies to any component of the vaccine"
expression.expression: Should vaccinate patient for Hib because no doses
